newsitem.title: MOROCCO: Moroccan Cbank withdraws 605 mln dirhams at repo.
newsitem.headline: Moroccan Cbank withdraws 605 mln dirhams at repo.

text.p: Morocco's Bank al-Maghrib (central bank) withdrew 605 million dirhams from the money market for one week at its repurchase auction, a bank official said on Thursday.

The bank received bids totalling 3.606 billion dirhams and allocated 3.390 billion dirhams at 6.5 percent interest rate. That was less than the 3.995 billion dirhams leaving the market this week, the official said.
It satisfied 94 percent percent of the demand for liquidity.
The next auction is due on February 5, 1997.
